defaultIn addition the generation of heat locally through energy from waste schemes within some urban areas has in cases helped alleviate the problem of urban waste disposal whilst s
defaultimultaneously helping provide low cost heating locally. Over recent years the Coventry Energy from waste plant has led to notable reductions in the volumes of waste destined for landfill through the increased heat recovery from such waste.
