defaultQuestion: defaultThermal storage is a potential useful method of balancing electricity/energy demdefaultand both diurnally and annually.default&#xa0;default What is government policy doing to promote thermal storage, and should it do more/different?default&#xa0;defaultResponse: defaultThe UKDEA agrees that thermal storage is a potentially useful method of bala
